article_title: Everything you need to know this lunchtime.
sentence: Overnight,  Israeli  strikes  in  Rafah  reportedly  killed  at  least  19  people,  while  four  Israeli  soldiers  were  killed  in  a  Hamas  rocket  attack  near  the  Kerem  Shalom  crossing  -  near  one  of  the  main  crossings  used  to  deliver  aid  into  Gaza.
